<subSubSection pageId="210" pageNumber="488" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="210.[177,1386,299,686]" pageId="210" pageNumber="488">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[179,313,453,486]" pageId="210" pageNumber="488">Breeding.</emphasis>
Two female Cariri Climbing Rats each had four embryos in late July; six of seven males captured between mid-August and early September had enlarged testes.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
